and American world champion Tom Jager the bronze in 22.30. Jager was silver
medallist behind Biondi in Seoul. Victory gave the Unified Team golds in all
the men's individual freestyle events from 50m to 400m, with Popov victor in
the 50m and 100m and Evgeny Sadovyi champion in the 200m and 400m. They also
won the 4 x 200m freestyle relay in world record time.
