</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
EXECUTIVE salary rises have fallen from an average of 7 per cent in 1991 to
5 per cent this year, according to the PA Consulting Group's latest Survey
of Executive Benefits. The annual average salary in the chief
executive/managing director group is Pounds 164,961.
